This product includes data derived from publicly-available filament
profiles published by upstream sources. Where data is treated as fact
(numerical chemistry values: temperatures, flow ratios, densities,
volumetric speeds), it is re-derived into this project's own canonical
schema rather than copied verbatim. Where this project distributes
verbatim third-party data files (under input/ for research staging),
those files retain their original copyright and license; this
project's Apache-2.0 license applies only to original work in this
repository.

Acknowledged upstream sources of chemistry values used in derivation:

  Bambu Lab -- Bambu Studio (https://github.com/bambulab/BambuStudio)
    AGPL-3.0; chemistry values referenced as facts, structure
    re-derived for this repository.

  Polymaker -- Polymaker-published Bambu Studio presets and TDS PDFs
    (https://polymaker.com)

  eSUN -- eSUN-published Bambu Studio HS-Parameters bundle and TDS
    PDFs (https://www.esun3d.com)

  Overture -- Overture-published Bambu Studio / Orca / Elegoo presets
    (https://overture3d.com/pages/download)

  Prusa Research -- PrusaSlicer system profiles
    (https://github.com/prusa3d/PrusaSlicer)
    AGPL-3.0; chemistry values referenced as facts, structure
    re-derived for this repository.

  Mark's Maker Space -- 3dfilamentprofiles.com (referenced for
    cross-validation only; no data imported)
